    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_2275605054120242231.png",
                "id": "talent52393",
                "key": "Sharpshooter",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sharpshooter"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Baron Bunny</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/8a097a3894f79e8b2dd0f81472461771_5389098407938057986.png",
                "id": "talent29674",
                "key": "Explosive Puppet",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Explosive Puppet"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin<span style=\"color: #FF9999\"> Pyro DMG </span>kepada target dan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Piercing DMG</span> kepada semua Karakter standby lawan.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/b470a6399635e18331542458f1dad94e_8337921644251082798.png",
                "id": "talent10842",
                "key": "Fiery Rain",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fiery Rain"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter aktifmu menerima DMG:</span> Mengurangi 2 poin DMG yang diterima.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span>.</p><p>Saat Penggunaan-nya habis, kartu ini tidak akan langsung dibuang.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Jika <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya sudah habis, Kartu ini dibuang dan mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7741560148324630597.png",
                "id": "talent33176",
                "key": "Baron Bunny",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/73a2f9790672a39cb2f9a87b5f09ed6b_8355053026841728085.png",
                "title": "Baron Bunny"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Pyro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>]<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan sekali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4808734853816874557.png",
                "id": "talent73404",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG tidak dapat dipengaruhi oleh Bonus DMG apa pun, namun tidak dapat ditahan oleh efek seperti Perisai atau kekebalan DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4664642989120680873.png",
                "id": "talent97947",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
